MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2013-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 15th December, 2013
The undersigned is directed to say that consequent on the demise of Shri Sis Ram Ola,
Minister of Labour and Employment on the 15th December, 2013, Shri Oscar Fernandes
assumed the additional charge of the office of the Minister of Labour and Employment, with
immediate effect. He will continue to hold the charge of the office of the Minister of Road
Transport and Highways.
